# Design Principles

The Trust Receipt module follows five guiding principles.

## Transparency

Every operational decision should be understandable.

## Explainability

Every stage of the decision journey should be visible.

## Verifiability

Users should be able to independently inspect recorded information.

## Integrity

Cryptographic references preserve decision integrity.

## Permanence

Every Trust Receipt becomes part of a permanent history of transparent operational decisions.

